<h3>Exploring the code of this demo site you will learn:</h3>

<ol class="round">
    <li class="one">
        <h5>Register assets in the BundleConfig.cs file</h5>
		In code of the <code>BundleConfig.cs</code> file, which is located in the folder <code>App_Start</code> you will see examples of how you can register the assets with help of methods <code>Include</code> and <code>IncludeDirectory</code> of class <code>Bundle</code>.
    </li>
    <li class="two">
        <h5>Configure Bundle Transformer and its separate modules</h5>
        In the <code>Web.config</code> file, you will see an example of advanced settings of Bundle Transformer and its separate modules.
    </li>
    <li class="three">
        <h5>See the results of work of translators and minifiers</h5>
        During viewing of output CSS- and JavaScript-code, you can see the result of work of translators and minifiers.
    </li>
</ol>